    prayer: `Father, I call on all that is within me to bless Your holy name. Forgive my forgetfulness. Help me remember Your benefits — Your forgiveness, Your healing, Your daily kindness — and let that remembering rise up as praise. Bless the Lord, O my soul. In the name of Jesus Christ. Amen.`,
